<div class="Parallax GParallax1"><div class="Img Binary"><div class="Caption"><a href="#"><div class="Text">Apprendre l'électronique<br></div></a></div></div><div class="Body2 Orange">Le but de ce tutoriel est de vous apprendre l'<b>électronique </b>appliquée aux sciences de l'ingénieur.<br>Produit par <b>Gérard KESSE</b>.<br><br><div class="Content0 GSummary1"><div class="Body0" id="Loader_1529412976174"><div class="Row26">Summary 1</div></div><script>loadSummary1("Loader_1529412976174");</script></div></div></div><br><div class="Content2 GTitle1"><div class="MainBlock2"><div class="Content"><h1 class="Title2 Center" id="Introduction"><a class="Link3" href="#">Introduction</a></h1><div class="Body3">L'<b>Électronique</b> est une branche de la physique appliquée, utilisant l'électricité comme support pour le traitement, la transmission et le stockage d'informations au sens large (son, image, commande). <br><br><div class="Img3 GImage"><img src="/data/img/defaults/banner_electronics.png" alt="/data/img/defaults/banner_electronics.png"></div><br></div></div></div></div><br><div class="Content2 GTitle1"><div class="MainBlock2"><div class="Content"><h1 class="Title2 Center" id="Circuit RC"><a class="Link3" href="#">Circuit RC</a></h1><div class="Body3"><br><div class="Content0 GSummary2"><div class="Body0" id="Loader_1620603976302"><div class="Row26">Summary 2</div></div><script>loadSummary2("Loader_1620603976302");</script></div><br><h2 class="Title7 GTitle2" id="Circuit RC-Schéma"><a class="Link9" href="#Circuit RC">Schéma</a></h2><br><br><h2 class="Title7 GTitle2" id="Circuit RC-Équation différentielle"><a class="Link9" href="#Circuit RC">Équation différentielle</a></h2><br><div class="Formula GFormula1"><div class="Formula2">\begin{eqnarray}
v_R+v_C &amp;=&amp; v_E\\
v_R &amp;=&amp; Ri\\
i &amp;=&amp; C\dfrac{dv_C}{dt}\\
Ri+v_C &amp;=&amp; v_E\\
RC\dfrac{dv_C}{dt}+v_C &amp;=&amp; v_E\\
\tau &amp;=&amp; RC\\
\tau\dfrac{dv_C}{dt}+v_C &amp;=&amp; v_E\\
v_C &amp;=&amp; v_{Ch}+v_{Cp}\\
\tau\dfrac{dv_{Ch}}{dt}+v_{Ch} &amp;=&amp; 0\\
\tau\dfrac{dv_{Ch}}{dt} &amp;=&amp; -v_{Ch}\\
\dfrac{dv_{Ch} }{v_{Ch}} &amp;=&amp; -\dfrac{dt}{\tau}\\
\int \dfrac{dv_{Ch} }{v_{Ch}} &amp;=&amp; -\int \dfrac{dt}{\tau}\\
\ln{v_{Ch}} &amp;=&amp; -\dfrac{t}{\tau} + A\\
\mathrm{e}^{\ln{v_{Ch}}} &amp;=&amp; {\mathrm{e}}^{\left(-\dfrac{t}{\tau} + A\right)}\\
v_{Ch} &amp;=&amp; A\mathrm{e}^{-\dfrac{t}{\tau}}
\end{eqnarray}</div></div><br></div></div></div></div><br><div class="Content2 GTitle1"><div class="MainBlock2"><div class="Content"><h1 class="Title2 Center" id="Électronique analogique"><a class="Link3" href="#">Électronique analogique</a></h1><div class="Body3"><br><h2 class="Title7 GTitle2" id="Électronique analogique-Table des matières"><a class="Link9" href="#Électronique analogique">Table des matières</a></h2><br><div class="Content0 GList1"><div class="Body0" id="Loader_1598425224409"><div class="Row26">List 1 &gt; Electronics &gt; analog</div></div><script>loadList1("Loader_1598425224409","Electronics","analog");</script></div><br></div></div></div></div><br>